":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T19:35:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dBEGfRZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdBEGfRZ.jpg&h=0e16ae4f&s={SIZE}\" />唔好意思借個位嚟<br />\n好重要今晚就係啦！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n*已獲不反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n~~~~~~~<br />\n<br />\n【<span style=\"color: red;\">國際人權日．正日集會</span>】<br />\n<br />\n1948年12月10日，聯合國公佈《世界人權宣言》，確立生而為人的基本權利。走過71年，世界人權仍然是未竟之路。在香港及世界各地，人民仍要為爭取基本的自由及權利奮鬥，甚至有所付出及犧牲。<br />\n<br />\n12月10日晚，我們一起站出來，為香港人加油，也為全球為人權奮鬥的人打氣。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n日期：12月10日<br />\n時間：18:30-22:00<br />\n地點：金鐘連儂牆下</span><br />\n<br />\n內容：<br />\n悼念及回顧<br />\n嘉賓講話<br />\n短片欣賞及分享<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TLBJubU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTLBJubU.jpg&h=dba2aa56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n推呀屌你再過20個鐘就係啦 唔好再屌鬼啦行動post呢文宣post呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係完咗人權日遊行就end game㗎<br />\n我地仲有訴求㗎！！！<br />\n聽日要見到連儂牆有十萬人呀！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n12月10號 6點半政總見！！"},{"pid":"ca9e99e061b6a0989229bf4bca6a5332870f7dea","tid":1776804,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T19:42:32.000Z","msg":"聽佢D語氣其實似港豬/中立撚.......多過藍絲....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n#要不是蛋哥護住佢"},{"pid":"b51b7fbb53ee8827d3d0ec8c3782376049e38c16","tid":1776804,"uid":100150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T19:54:45.000Z","msg":"今日旺角好歡樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8448f0472b44264ceaa4a04b8469f856ea70121f","tid":1776804,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ca9e99e061b6a0989229bf4bca6a5332870f7dea","tid":1776804,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T1